---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section
   id="precos"
   class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-24 sm:px-6"
   aria-label="Comece agora"
>
   <div class="mb-10 flex flex-col gap-3">
      <h2
         class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em] text-foreground sm:text-5xl"
      >
         CTA Sem Vergonha
      </h2>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg">
         Se nada disso te convenceu, talvez essas táticas clássicas de
         marketing convençam.
      </p>
   </div>

   <div
      class="relative grid gap-12 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-border/60 bg-card/40 p-8 backdrop-blur-xl lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr] lg:p-14"
   >
      <div
         class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-50"
         style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 0%, oklch(0.7729 0.1535 163.2231 / 0.18), transparent 55%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 100%, oklch(0.72 0.22 340 / 0.18), transparent 55%);"
         aria-hidden="true"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col gap-4">
         <div
            class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-blue-500/90 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white shadow-lg"
         >
            <span>3 pessoas</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-normal opacity-80"
               >(quase) adicionaram Montte ao carrinho*</span
            >
         </div>
         <span class="text-[10px] text-muted-foreground/70 italic">
            *se isso fosse um carrinho de verdade
         </span>

         <div
            class="relative mt-2 aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/60 bg-gradient-to-br from-background/80 via-card/40 to-background/80"
         >
            <div
               class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]"
               style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, currentColor 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, currentColor 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 24px 24px;"
            >
            </div>

            <div
               class="absolute inset-8 flex flex-col gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border/60 bg-card/80 p-5 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur"
            >
               <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-red-400/80"></span>
                  <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-400/80"></span>
                  <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-green-400/80"></span>
                  <span class="ml-2 font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground"
                     >montte.app/dashboard</span
                  >
               </div>
               <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span
                     class="inline-flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/15 ring-1 ring-primary/30"
                  >
                     <Image class="size-5" src="/favicon.svg" alt="" width={20} height={20} />
                  </span>
                  <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5">
                     <span class="text-sm font-bold text-foreground">Montte 2026</span>
                     <span class="text-[10px] text-muted-foreground"
                        >ERP brasileiro com IA · v2026.05</span
                     >
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-border/40 pt-3">
                  {
                     [
                        "✓ Financeiro conciliado",
                        "✓ 2.847 contatos importados",
                        "✓ Rubi categorizou 98%",
                        "✓ Fatura emitida via Pix",
                     ].map((line) => (
                        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-foreground/80">
                           {line}
                        </span>
                     ))
                  }
               </div>
            </div>

            <div
               class="absolute -top-2 -right-4 rotate-12 rounded-full bg-orange-400 px-4 py-3 text-center text-[11px] font-bold text-orange-950 shadow-xl"
               style="clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 61% 19%, 81% 8%, 73% 28%, 95% 30%, 78% 45%, 100% 55%, 78% 65%, 95% 80%, 73% 78%, 81% 100%, 61% 87%, 50% 100%, 39% 87%, 19% 100%, 27% 78%, 5% 80%, 22% 65%, 0% 55%, 22% 45%, 5% 30%, 27% 28%, 19% 8%, 39% 19%);"
            >
               <span class="block leading-tight">
                  NÃO<br />ENDOSSADO<br />POR<br />NEYMAR
               </span>
            </div>

            <div
               class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 flex flex-col items-center rounded-md bg-background/90 p-2 shadow-lg ring-1 ring-border/60"
            >
               <span class="text-[8px] font-bold tracking-wider text-foreground">G2</span>
               <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-foreground">Líder</span>
               <span
                  class="mt-1 rounded-sm bg-red-500 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[7px] font-bold text-white"
                  >2026</span
               >
            </div>
         </div>
         <p class="text-center text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground italic">
            *Montte é um produto web e não pode ser instalado por CD. Já mandamos
            um disquete uma vez, mas era um Rickroll.
         </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col gap-6">
         <span
            class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md bg-primary px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-primary-foreground shadow"
         >
            <svg
               class="size-3"
               viewBox="0 0 24 24"
               fill="currentColor"
               aria-hidden="true"
               ><path
                  d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 21.34l1.89.66.95-2.3c.48.17.98.3 1.34.3 6 0 10-3.5 10-9 0-2-1-3-1-3z"
               ></path></svg
            >
            ECO-FRIENDLY
         </span>

         <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <h3 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] text-foreground sm:text-6xl">
               Montte Cloud
            </h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Download digital*</span>
         </div>

         <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Onde rodar:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
               <button
                  type="button"
                  class="rounded-lg border-2 border-foreground bg-background px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-foreground"
               >
                  BR (São Paulo)
               </button>
               <button
                  type="button"
                  class="rounded-lg border-2 border-border/40 bg-transparent px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:border-border"
               >
                  Self-hosted
               </button>
            </div>
         </div>

         <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">A partir de:</span>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
               <span class="text-2xl text-muted-foreground line-through">R$0</span>
               <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary sm:text-4xl">
                  GRÁTIS
               </span>
               <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                  &gt;1 vaga ainda nesse preço!!
               </span>
            </div>
         </div>

         <a
            href="/dashboard"
            class="group inline-flex h-16 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-primary px-8 text-xl font-bold text-primary-foreground shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/40"
         >
            Começar agora
         </a>

         <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border/60 bg-background/40 p-4 backdrop-blur">
            <span
               class="inline-flex size-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/15 text-primary ring-1 ring-primary/30"
            >
               <svg
                  class="size-4"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M3 17l6-6 4 4 8-8"></path><path d="M14 7h7v7"></path></svg
               >
            </span>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground">
               <span class="font-bold">Corre:</span> dezenas de empresas se
               cadastraram <span class="font-bold text-primary">hoje</span>.
               Aproveite e ganhe <span class="font-bold">R$0 de desconto</span>
               na primeira fatura.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</section>
